    <!-- ABOUT PRODUCTION -->
    <section class="space-y-12 mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium">About Production</h2>

        <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-stone-400 uppercase mb-2">Brief Description</h3>
            <p>
                “Puzzle Piece” is an emotional-design visual exploring connection, alignment, 
                and the quiet moment something finally “clicks.” The four-part series builds toward 
                <strong>Piece 315 — THE CLICK</strong>, symbolizing inner clarity.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-stone-400 uppercase mb-2">Creative Problem</h3>
            <p>
                The challenge: communicate emotional clarity without interaction or animation—only still visuals. 
                The project needed to express subtle emotional resonance using composition, spacing, 
                tone, and metaphor.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-stone-400 uppercase mb-2">Solution</h3>
            <p>
                Puzzle pieces became the metaphor for emotional alignment. Each part represents a stage in 
                emotional understanding. Soft tones, minimal layout, and quiet spacing support the reflective, 
                introspective feeling.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PROCESS -->
    <section class="space-y-12 mb-20">
